WEBVTT

00:00:00.429 --> 00:00:02.405
Track 06.06

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:06.122
Dan: Would you like a cup of tea?

00:00:06.479 --> 00:00:07.733
Eva: Yes, please.

00:00:08.381 --> 00:00:10.476
Dan: And would you like a piece of cake?

00:00:10.587 --> 00:00:12.865
Eva: No, it’s OK, thanks.

00:00:13.394 --> 00:00:15.878
Dan: I need to go to the shops for bread.

00:00:16.378 --> 00:00:17.703
Eva: I’ll come with you.

00:00:18.176 --> 00:00:20.271
Dan: That’s great, thanks.

00:00:20.732 --> 00:00:22.914
And I need to make some sandwiches.

00:00:23.055 --> 00:00:24.206
Eva: I’ll help you.

00:00:24.380 --> 00:00:26.587
Dan: Thank you, that’s very kind.